criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  BTSS confirmed by two of magnetic resonance venography (MRV), computed tomography
             venography (CTV) or digital subtraction angiography (DSA).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  medicine related intracranial hypertension;

          -  systemic inflammation;

          -  moderate to severe stenosis in intracranial, carotid or vertebral arteries;

          -  moderate to severe stenosis in intracranial or jugular veins other than transverse
             sinus;

          -  intracranial lesions.
